#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2025-07-23-secure-mcp-oidc-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus-mcp-server` client represents a confidential OIDC client that protects the MCP server."
msgstr "O cliente `quarkus-mcp-server` representa um cliente OIDC confidencial que protege o servidor MCP."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2025-07-23-secure-mcp-oidc-client.adoc
#, fuzzy
